queries.sql: SELECT CASE WHEN (@@OPTIONS | 256) = @@OPTIONS THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS qi

SELECT sekolah_id as instansi_id,'' as kode_instansi, s.nama as nama_sekolah, s.nama as nama, npsn, s.kode_wilayah as kode_wilayah, status_sekolah, r1.nama as provinsi, r2.nama as kota, r3.nama as kecamatan FROM [arsip].[dbo].[sekolah] s LEFT JOIN Referensi.ref.mst_wilayah r1 on LEFT(r1.kode_wilayah, 2) = LEFT (s.kode_wilayah, 2) AND r1.id_level_wilayah=1 LEFT JOIN Referensi.ref.mst_wilayah r2 on LEFT(r2.kode_wilayah, 4) = LEFT (s.kode_wilayah, 4) AND r2.id_level_wilayah=2 LEFT JOIN Referensi.ref.mst_wilayah r3 on LEFT(r3.kode_wilayah, 6) = LEFT (s.kode_wilayah, 6) AND r3.id_level_wilayah=3 WHERE npsn = '10646570'

select w1.nama as kelurahan,w2.nama as kecamatan, w3.nama as kota, w4.nama as propinsi, w1.id_level_wilayah, w1.mst_kode_wilayah, w1.kode_wilayah 
		from Referensi.ref.mst_wilayah w1, Referensi.ref.mst_wilayah w2, Referensi.ref.mst_wilayah w3, Referensi.ref.mst_wilayah w4 
		where w1.kode_wilayah = '116104AA' and (w1.mst_kode_wilayah = w2.kode_wilayah) and 
		(w2.mst_kode_wilayah = w3.kode_wilayah) and (w3.mst_kode_wilayah = w4.kode_wilayah)
		order by w1.id_level_wilayah, w2.nama, w1.nama

SELECT * FROM [arsip].[dbo].[ptk_terdaftar] ptk1 LEFT JOIN arsip.dbo.ptk ptk ON ptk.ptk_id=ptk1.ptk_id where ptk.aktif=1 AND ptk1.jenis_ptk_id=20 AND ptk1.sekolah_id='C75F3117-CF66-438E-A2DA-8C13887E7AD9' AND tahun_ajaran_id = (SELECT MAX(tahun_ajaran_id) FROM Referensi.ref.tahun_ajaran WHERE expired_date IS NULL) AND ptk1.Soft_delete=0 AND ptk1.jenis_keluar_id IS NULL ORDER BY ptk1.ptk_induk DESC, CASE WHEN ptk1.ptk_induk = 1 THEN 0 ELSE 1 END, tanggal_surat_tugas DESC

SELECT (CASE WHEN UPPER(peran_ang) LIKE 'PELINDUNG%' THEN 1 WHEN UPPER(peran_ang) LIKE 'PEMBINA%' THEN 2 WHEN UPPER(peran_ang) LIKE 'PENGARAH%' THEN 3 WHEN UPPER(peran_ang) LIKE 'PENANGGUNG%' THEN 4 WHEN UPPER(peran_ang) LIKE 'KETUA%' THEN 5 WHEN UPPER(peran_ang) LIKE 'WAKIL%' THEN 6 WHEN UPPER(peran_ang) LIKE 'SEKRETARIS%' THEN 7 WHEN UPPER(peran_ang) LIKE 'BENDAHARA%' THEN 8 WHEN UPPER(peran_ang) LIKE 'HUMAS%' THEN 9 WHEN UPPER(peran_ang) LIKE 'KOOR%' THEN 10 WHEN UPPER(peran_ang) LIKE 'KORD%' THEN 11 WHEN UPPER(peran_ang) LIKE 'SEKSI%' THEN 12 ELSE 13 END ) AS urutan, (CASE WHEN k.ptk_id is NULL THEN 0 ELSE 1 END) AS urutan2, ua.nama as nama_unsur2,s.nama as nama_sekolah,l.ptk_id_anggota_1,l.ptk_id_anggota_2,l.ptk_id_anggota_3,k.sk_tugas as nomor_sk,* FROM [TPPK].[dbo].[kepanitiaan] k LEFT JOIN TPPK.dbo.ref_unsur_anggota ua ON ua.id_unsur_anggota = k.unsur_ang LEFT JOIN Arsip.dbo.ptk p ON p.ptk_id = k.ptk_id LEFT JOIN Arsip.dbo.sekolah s ON s.sekolah_id = p.sekolah_id LEFT JOIN [Referensi].[ref].[jenis_ptk] r ON r.jenis_ptk_id = p.jenis_ptk_id LEFT JOIN [TPPK].[dbo].[login_tppk] l ON l.sk_tugas = k.sk_tugas WHERE k.sekolah_id = 'C75F3117-CF66-438E-A2DA-8C13887E7AD9' AND soft_delete_kepanitiaan=0 AND soft_delete_anggota_panitia=0 AND tmt_sk_tugas = (SELECT MAX(tmt_sk_tugas) FROM [TPPK].[dbo].[kepanitiaan] WHERE sekolah_id = 'C75F3117-CF66-438E-A2DA-8C13887E7AD9' AND soft_delete_kepanitiaan=0 AND soft_delete_anggota_panitia=0) AND (tst_sk_tugas IS NULL OR tst_sk_tugas = (SELECT MAX(tst_sk_tugas) FROM [TPPK].[dbo].[kepanitiaan] WHERE sekolah_id = 'C75F3117-CF66-438E-A2DA-8C13887E7AD9' AND soft_delete_kepanitiaan = 0 AND soft_delete_anggota_panitia = 0)) ORDER BY urutan, urutan2 DESC, k.nm_ang ASC
